{"tid":1854054,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(正視聽)  點解林鄭會話內地旅客已大幅下跌百分之91 ???","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T10:02:37.000Z","uid":156096,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"870516ed4d5be2dfc2ce3fd516b10db7ece12a28","tid":1854054,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭公佈，截至今日（31日）上午9時，確診個案總數為12宗，當中1宗需要調查是否外地輸入；目前有191宗懷疑個案仍然需要住院接受檢查。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭以過去14日作比較，稱實施「局部封關」後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內地旅客已大幅下跌百分之91；林鄭僅稱會在口岸新增健康申報表</span></strong>，堅拒全面禁止內地人入境香港。<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解林鄭會話內地旅客已大幅下跌百分之91 ???</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好明顯佢唔係同香港人講，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢係同緊國際社會講</span>。<br />\n<br />\n 大家仲記唔得得上次佢講局部封關，香港人屌到佢仆街，但<span style=\"color: red;\">外國傳媒比佢昆左，以為真係封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次佢又食過返尋味，講跌91% ，想唔得罪中國得尼，又可以避開國際傳媒，等國際社會誤以為佢做左野。<br />\n所以，大家千其<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好係香港圍爐屌就算，一定要比全世界知7 婆有幾陰毒有幾賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下國際戰線手足又好，twitter手足又好，一定要同全世界講清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同就幫手推推post<im